      "title": "Death Star Thinking and Government Reform",
      "url": "https://jods.mitpress.mit.edu/pub/issue3-pahlka/release/2",
      "publishedDate": "2016-09-01",
      "readDate": "2026-03-18",
      "language": "en",
      "abstract": "The article discusses the complexities of government reform and critiques the 'Death Star thinking' approach, which assumes that problems can be solved with a single, well-placed solution. It explores real-world examples and suggests alternative approaches to government reform.",
